#* {{quote-book|en|year=2011| title=Slovakia in History |author=Mikuláš Teich, ‎Dušan Kováč, ‎Martin D. Brown | page=42| passage=Fortifications and '''town''' walls clearly highlight the central military significance of '''towns'''. }}
